#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""Run FragAnnotor benchmark against CFM-ID, SIRIUS, and MS2DeepScore.

The pipeline supports:

* PFAS locked-test candidate matrices generated by the companion
  transformation-product workflow.
* CASMI 2022 processed splits if present under data/casmi_2022 or supplied via
  --casmi-dir. The script reports CASMI as unavailable instead of fabricating a
  standard test split when the required files are absent.

All model calls go through the BaseAnnotator-compatible wrappers in baselines/.
"""

